[122.251689, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
[122.251921, "o", "\u001b[38;2;157;169;160m  89\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;157;169;160m│\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;62;71;77m-\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m \u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77mDiversify institutional borrower exposure and require over-collateralisation with real-time margin calls — single-counterparty concentration killed BlockFi.\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n:\u001b[K"]
[122.292214, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
[122.292363, "o", "\u001b[38;2;157;169;160m  90\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;157;169;160m│\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;62;71;77m-\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m Register yield-bearing accounts with the SEC and relevant state regulators before scaling; BlockFi's $100M settlement weakened it structurally before any market shock hit.\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n:\u001b[K"]
[122.317167, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
[122.317252, "o", "\u001b[38;2;157;169;160m  91\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;157;169;160m│\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;62;71;77m-\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m Maintain liquid reserves sufficient to honour withdrawals during a 30-day contagion event; BlockFi had to halt withdrawals immediately when FTX froze.\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n:\u001b[K"]
[122.351132, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
[122.351286, "o", "\u001b[38;2;157;169;160m  92\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;157;169;160m│\u001b[0m \u001b[38;2;62;71;77m-\u001b[0m\u001b[38;2;62;71;77m Keep uninsured cash at multiple FDIC-insured institutions and diversify banking relationships to avoid a second-order loss channel (cf. BlockFi's $227M at SVB).\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n:\u001b[K"]
[122.387296, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
